### 🧪 Entity Framework Core ORM HTTP Test Client

# Konfigurasi Environment
@hostname = localhost
@port = 5000
@host = http://{{hostname}}:{{port}}

###
# 1. Eager Loading (Mengambil Produk + JOIN Category)
GET {{host}}/api/orm/products-eager

###

# 2. Explicit Loading (Mengambil Produk dan memuat Category secara manual)
GET {{host}}/api/orm/product-explicit/1

###

# 3. Read Only Query (Menggunakan AsNoTracking)
GET {{host}}/api/orm/products-readonly

###

# 4. Update Price (Mengamati perubahan State Change Tracker)
PUT {{host}}/api/orm/update-price/2?newPrice=900000

###

# 5. Raw SQL Query (Aman dari SQL Injection)
GET {{host}}/api/orm/raw-sql?minPrice=500000
